Issues.Body:
Affects the following example:
```cs
int formatId = RegisterClipboardFormat(new string('a', 255);
DataFormats.Format format = DataFormats.GetFormat(formatId);
Console.WriteLine(format.Name);
```

It prints out a 127 long string rather than the original 255 length

E.g. in ListBox.cs

```cs
static bool RunningOnWin2K {
    get {
        if (!checkedOS) {
            if (Environment.OSVersion.Platform != System.PlatformID.Win32NT ||
                Environment.OSVersion.Version.Major < 5) {
                runningOnWin2K = false;
                checkedOS = true;
            }
        }
        return runningOnWin2K;
    }
}

```
